1. Nisam siguran da li mogu da *zamenim* svoj termin za tvoj (I'm not sure if I can *replace* my appointment with yours)
2. Da li možeš da mi *zameniš* mesto u redu? (Can you *exchange* places with me in line?)
3. Moramo da *zamenimo* ulje u automobilu. (We need to *change* the oil in the car.)
4. Hoću da *zamenim* ovu majicu za drugu veličinu. (I want to *exchange* this shirt for a different size.)
5. Ako mi *zameniš* mesto u restoranu, kupujem ti piće. (If you *switch* seats with me in the restaurant, I'll buy you a drink.)
6. Nisam uspeo da *zamenim* novac u banci danas. (I wasn't able to *exchange* money at the bank today.)
7. Molim te da *zameniš* baterije u daljinskom upravljaču. (Please *replace* the batteries in the remote control.)
8. Hoću da *zamenim* ovu knjigu za drugu temu. (I want to *exchange* this book for a different topic.)
9. Nisam mogao da *zamenim* svoj let zbog lošeg vremena. (I couldn't *change* my flight because of bad weather.)
10. Da li si *zamislio* šta bi se dogodilo ako ne bismo *zamenili* ovaj deo? (Have you *imagined* what would happen if we didn't *replace* this part?)